'''Rainbow Falls''' is a perennial plunge waterfall located near [[Harrison Lake]], [[British Columbia]].<ref>[http://www.waterfallsnorthwest.com/bc_waterfall.php?num=380&p=0 Rainbow Falls | Waterfalls of the Pacific Northwest]</ref> The falls can be viewed with difficulty from a bridge on the unpaved logging road below.

